overview:
Kerry is responsible for managing the operations at Selby and everything that entails including executive support, investor relations, event planning, facilities/IT management, HR, and accounts receivables/payables. Prior to joining Selby in 1999, Kerry held a number of executive support positions at companies including DCM/Doll Capital Management, Summit Partners, Sybase, and Cornerstone Properties.

Kerry is a native Californian, having grown up in Marin County. She enjoys going to the beach with her two dogs, traveling with friends, spending time with family, and hitting the driving range to work on her swing.
